notes:
This dataset contains distribution of telephone subscribers i.e Nepal telecom limited, United Telecom Limited, Ncell Pvt Ltd, STM Telecom Sanchar Pvt. Ltd, Nepal Satellite Telecom Pvt.,  Smart Telecom and others. This dataset was extracted from Eco Survey published by Ministry of finance on 2013/14.
Link : http://www.mof.gov.np/en/archive-documents/economic-survey-21.html
